column3:
Germinating Quantity

If you have any seeds that are germinating of this species in your nursery input that quantity here. Only enter numbers or an error will occur during upload.
column4:
Seedling Quantity

This number will add inventory with the "active growth" status in Terraware. Only enter numbers or an error will occur during upload.
column5:
Stored Date*
Please enter in YYYY-MM-DD format or an error will occur during upload. If you are unsure of the exact date an estimate is fine!
column6:
Sub-Locations
If seedlings are in more than one sub-location, separate the sub-location names with line breaks.
